Package com.st.st25sdk.type4a

Provides classes to handle NFC Forum Type4 Family Tags and Dynamic Tags.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    STType4CounterInterface
    Defines common methods to be implemented for STmicroelectronics Type4 tags embedding a counter
    STType4GpoInterface
    Defines an API to handle a STMicroelectronics type4 tag featuring a GPO
    STType4PasswordInterface
    Defines an API to handle a STMicroelectronics Type4 tag featuring passwords
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CCFileType4
    This class defines all required methods to handle a NFC Forum Type4 Capability Container file.
    ControlTlv
    Defines all required methods to handle a NFC Forum Type4 CCfile TLV block
    FileType4
    Defines all required methods shared by NFC Forum Type4 files
    NdefFileType4
    Defines all required methods to handle a NFC Forum Type4 NDEF file.
    STSysFileType4
    Defines all required methods to handle a STmicroelectronics Type4 System file
    STType4MultiAreaTag
    Defines all required methods to handle a STmicroelectronics type4 tag supporting multiple areas
    STType4Tag
    Defines all required methods to handle a STMicroelectronics Type4 tag
    SysFileType4
    Base class for Type4 System file classes
    Type4Tag
    Defines required methods to handle a NFC Forum Type4 tag
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    STType4GpoInterface.GpoMode
    List of all the possible GPO modes.
    Type4Tag.AccessStatus
    Lists type4 Access Status
    Type4Tag.Type4FileType
    Lists existing Type4 file types
